    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust spots, several large dents, and paint that has faded significantly due to sun exposure. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and several interior components are cracked or missing. Mechanically, the car is currently running but requires immediate repairs to the suspension and exhaust system to be considered roadworthy. This is an ideal candidate for a full restoration project or for use as a parts vehicle.",
